            "title": "No Evidence of Hendra Virus Infection in the Australian Flying‐fox Ectoparasite Genus Cyclopodia",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "M. E.",
                    "lastName": "Vidgen"
                },
                {
